              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">DGT Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/c5f5c789f46baf1c0c0ff52d5feabe9a_5079786229871650390.png",
                "id": "talent720",
                "key": "Rite : Traversée abyssale",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rite : Traversée abyssale"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 4 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">DGT Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Niv. de Possession </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">éclaireur sermenté</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+2.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Éclaireur sermenté</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase final : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Cumule 1 niv. de Possession.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Accorde les effets suivants selon le niv. de Possession :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 2 : Les </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">DGT physiques</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> sont convertis en </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">DGT Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 4 : DGT infligés +2.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 6 : Niv. de Possession -4.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/b6ab0891aede70ddf48bfa3859de14ea_8968682183298186853.png",
                "id": "talent5953",
                "key": "Liturgie : Rapidité lupine",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Liturgie : Rapidité lupine"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Capacité passive</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">(Passif) Accorde un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">éclaireur sermenté </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">au début du combat.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Éclaireur sermenté</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase final : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Cumule 1 niv. de Possession.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Accorde les effets suivants selon le niv. de Possession :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 2 : Les </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">DGT physiques</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> sont convertis en </span><span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">DGT Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 4 : DGT infligés +2.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Supérieur ou égal à 6 : Niv. de Possession -4.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/8a173f8df2e58a9df74a6c3a74d385eb_6614362303084839368.png",
                "id": "talent67477",
                "key": "Exécution légale",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Exécution légale"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Électro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Surcharge </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +2 et bascule de force la cible pour le personnage suivant</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Supraconduction </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Électrocution </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et inflige 1 pt de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autre que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Stimulation </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et crée un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">champ catalyseur</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> qui augmente les 3 prochains coups de DGT Dendro/Électro de 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_5809084644079313836.png",
